Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:09.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:10.90,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:12.24,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:13.95,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:28.88,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:33.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:36.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:39.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu-chan, you're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:42.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life was in...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:46.98,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,L...Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:56.45,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:05.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done a wonderful\Njob of raising Ryuji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:12.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:14.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:17.51,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I raised him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.14,0:01:31.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was in a life-threatening accident.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:34.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, Ya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:36.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuji was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:40.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yasuko was completely fooled\Nby a fake message Taiga left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:47.08,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There was a lot of sobbing, and she\Ngot an earful from Grandpa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:52.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's like...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.17,0:01:55.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like Ya-chan's a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:59.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Families sure are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:04.81,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been well over ten years since they\Nlast saw each other, but they're still...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:06.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:08.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your fault for always spoiling her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:10.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, please. Why shouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:11.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:14.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:19.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Family...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:26.08,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.54,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a bath before the water gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:29.71,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:45.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You were never married?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:46.89,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,They told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:47.89,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:54.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Your daddy ran off with another woman\Nwhen I was pregnant with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:58.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone told me I shouldn't keep you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:02:59.90,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:05.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to protect you,\Nno matter what it took.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:08.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But...I failed in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:10.25,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's fallen apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:15.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:17.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You did a good job of raising me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:19.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I'm bigger than you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:22.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:25.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You've really grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:30.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked so big as I\Nwatched you running away...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:33.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I hardly recognized you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:35.98,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It scared me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And it made me kind of\Nhappy at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:44.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was scared of you leaving me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:47.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So you left me first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:50.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:57.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I'm in any position to talk, but\Nrunning away won't accomplish anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:58.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:00.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be more mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:02.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't do it somewhere far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:06.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to grow up right in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:08.81,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:10.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:16.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stop crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:18.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:20.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:28.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma said we might as well sleep in the\Nsame room, since we're getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:32.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She really must be to blame\Nfor how Yasuko turned out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya-chan's laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:35.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:39.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, turn off the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:40.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:42.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:45.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:47.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:51.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:55.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:05:01.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew running off and getting\Nmarried would never work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:05.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanted to dream a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:09.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Because everything would fall apart\Nagain if I didn't do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:12.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:13.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Yasuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:16.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's fallen apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:19.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And we can start from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:24.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to elope if we have\Npermission to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:28.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be best to have\Neveryone's support?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:31.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Like who?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa and Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:35.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That could take a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:42.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:44.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're going to be happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:49.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,we should share that happiness \Nwith the people around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:51.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:56.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But let's give it a test run.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:01.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:03.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A veil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:06.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Takasu Ryuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:13.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:17.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter. Whatever comes to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't just make something up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:20.81,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:23.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Take you, Aisaka Taiga—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:26.24,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget the vows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:28.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who wanted to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:32.24,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what you told me\Nback when we first met?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:33.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:35.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We are tiger and dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Said to stand together as\Nequals since ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:42.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need vows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:46.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we'll always be together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:48.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:51.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Tai—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes are bloodshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:54.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're breathing hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:58.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Your lips are chapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll hurt if we kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:01.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So I fail...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:07.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If we kiss, it'll probably hurt...a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:16.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,How was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.08,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly what I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:22.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Rough and dry as barren earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:27.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But also...burning hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:28.88,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:31.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty cold. Let's try again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:36.31,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:47.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.87,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:09.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels kinda weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just the two of us on the way here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:14.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbut there's three of us, plus one, going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:18.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You were convinced, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:21.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That Ya-chan would come\Nswooping in if we lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:24.90,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That she'd make up with your grandparents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:27.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say I was convinced.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:31.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But at the same time, I didn't\Nthink it was impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:32.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:36.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's just how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:39.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that's what it means to be a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:45.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:49.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga-chan, you'll come over for dinner, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:50.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:52.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, don't be shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a member of our family!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.43,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:00.51,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Aw, I didn't forget you!\N- Taiga...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:03.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Inko-chan, you're a family member too!\N- Go ahead. I need to get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't your mom in your...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:12.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:18.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:20.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:23.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm making your favorite,\Npork cutlets, tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:34.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:40.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.15,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Missed Calls: 47    Voicemail: 5    Inbox: 28
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:51.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Taiga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:53.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you think—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:56.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you understand the conse—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:57.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop thi—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:58.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Taiga...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:01.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Taiga, do you truly hate me this mu—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:08.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forget it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't give a damn what\Nyou do or where you go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:11.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm leaving!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:12.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have it your way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.21,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bye-bye, kid!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:24.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, she's so childish...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:28.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ryuji, you know...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:33.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I always believed that no one\Nwould ever love me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:35.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Smells good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:37.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:40.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma gave me a great\Nrecipe for stewed taro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:41.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:44.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ryu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:48.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I was probably just running away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:52.21,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't see any stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:55.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:11:00.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Useless and helpless, just like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:06.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I blamed my parents and circumstances\Nfor my lack of confidence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:12.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Ryuji, you loved me for who I am.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:14.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:18.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't run away anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:20.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll change.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:22.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll accept who I am...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:24.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and learn to be proud of myself...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:27.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so that I can give you my love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:33.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Taiga didn't show up for dinner that night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:38.42,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, we won't know what's\Ngoing on if you refuse to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What actually happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:40.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't Taiga—?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:43.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, class! Take your seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:48.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I have some bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:54.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to family reasons, Aisaka-san\Nwill be leaving our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:12:00.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just formally contacted by her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:02.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka-san will be going to live with her—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:03.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:05.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lie! A ruse! A sham!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:07.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But she didn't tell us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:12.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,As you go through life, you will all find\Nyourselves at various crossroads.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:14.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You may wish to stop where you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or turn back, but you'll \Nhave to make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:25.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka-san's decision...means\Nthat she had to leave you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:30.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure she tried to find\Nthe best possible solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:31.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We should support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:32.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:36.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:38.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids today terrify me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're calling Aisaka-san already!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:41.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Texting her!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:42.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:45.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- But...reflect on life! Savor each moment!\N- Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:48.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Back to your seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:01.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Kushie—\N- Better brace yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:05.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come back alone!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Taiga transferring!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:08.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:09.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Taka—!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:11.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:13.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:15.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:18.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to let her go...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:21.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could bring her back, I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:24.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why she would\Ndecide this without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:26.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:32.95,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She trusts me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:38.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So for now...all I can do is accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:42.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:55.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She finally learned to \Nclean up after herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:59.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What...is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:01.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! A lone sock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:02.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:04.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your partner!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:06.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:07.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:09.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That klutz...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:13.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She was supposed to take these with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.12,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Student Handbook
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:35.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You really are a klutz...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:42.98,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,New Message\NFrom: Taiga
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:46.86,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you never said you love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:46.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:49.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty sure that after I fell in the river...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:52.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We were interrupted...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:55.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Man... I even said it to\NKawashima a bunch of times...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:58.29,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Klutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:02.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one to talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:05.21,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Downloading
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:11.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomiie-kun, are you busy today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:12.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:14.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stop somewhere on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:15.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna come?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:17.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:18.31,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:29.45,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.25,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.25,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Except I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:46.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't say you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:52.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I get what you were saying, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:54.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:56.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A message from Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:56.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:57.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:58.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:00.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:03.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Taiga replied to\Neveryone who texted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:06.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did she only send a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:07.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, seaweed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:12.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:14.82,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:16.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:18.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So this tiny light is a star?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:19.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:21.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:23.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, I'm sure it's a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But why send a picture of the night sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:30.21,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,To let us know that she's always\Nwatching over us from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:32.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that! She's not dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:34.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's trying to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:36.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,that she won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:40.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when the sky's so dark \Nyou can't see a thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:44.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,there are still stars shining out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:49.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So if she can learn to shine brighter,\Nthen we'll be able to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:55.82,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say Taiga's being pretty selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:17:00.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But having said that, we all\Nlive under the same sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:06.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If each of us learns to shine, it won't\Nmatter how far apart we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:10.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to see each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:16.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so cheesy, I'm gonna hurl...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:18.43,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sent a chill down my spine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:19.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:21.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I like the sound of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:22.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:24.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what it means to be young?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:25.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:26.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:27.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:29.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:31.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,remember how a certain someone \Nmade a huge mess a while back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:33.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:34.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:39.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd probably make her happy\Nif we sent her a reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:41.08,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:43.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:44.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't find it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:46.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did we put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:49.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember putting it away\Nwith Ami-chan's tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:51.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:53.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:58.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to making others happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:01.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...really good at it, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:03.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:06.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,My very existence is a surprise in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:10.11,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to be jealous
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of how she was adored\Nwhen she was simply being herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:18.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:21.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that wasn't the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:26.25,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That little girl with a big attitude had a\Nheart as tiny and timid as her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:29.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She worried so much about\Nwhat other people thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:32.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,that she never let anyone see the real her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.42,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Reminds me of someone else I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:37.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, a certain someone who saw through\Nher facade from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:41.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that I was just a child, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:45.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I hated having to act like an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:49.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And it annoyed me when everyone\Nassumed that I was mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:51.90,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But after seeing Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:57.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that it didn't matter, as long as\None person out there understood me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:01.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they didn't love me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:03.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Kawashima...\N- Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:06.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I found the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:11.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:12.54,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I just press this button, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:13.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:15.25,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:18.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I lose my power as a Patron Saint!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:18.17,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka—Do your best!\NTIGER!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:20.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:21.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:25.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:27.43,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I am smiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:27.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Amin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:29.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:33.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am a dragon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:40.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are a tiger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:46.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And tigers and dragons have been\Nconsidered equals since ancient times.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:49.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So it doesn't matter...that you\Naren't here with me now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:52.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll transcend space and time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:55.21,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to always be by your side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:57.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My feelings...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}will never change.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:17.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's similar but different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:17.57,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,nitetemo chigauyo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:20.82,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,mandarin orenji
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:20.82,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Mandarines and oranges.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:24.45,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends and lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:24.45,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,tomodachi koibito
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:28.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The hearts of the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:28.20,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,futari no kokoromo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:34.71,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to be hurt, so I ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:34.71,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kizutsuki takunai watashi wa nigeteta
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:37.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And now the light
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:37.96,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,soshitara hikarimo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:42.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Inko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this lip gloss a bit too flashy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:46.51,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:48.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I should use a more natural color...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:51.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:52.31,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Inko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:58.98,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Inko-chan said her name!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:58.98,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Graduation Ceremony Notice
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:01.86,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohashi High School 78th\NGraduation Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:08.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm going to miss those\Nguys after graduation...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:11.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,They were a fun bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:11.04,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,47th Diploma Presentation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:13.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear about Kitamura-senpai,\Nthe student council president?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:16.21,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to study abroad\Nin America next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:17.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:22.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The president and his class helped make the\Nculture and athletic festivals so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:23.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:27.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard that last year's\NCulture Festival was the best ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:28.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, I heard that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:30.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary festival where\N2-C swept the contests?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:31.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:35.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all thanks to someone\Ncalled Palm-top-something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:36.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Palm-top-something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:38.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the Palm-top Tiger?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:40.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The one that brings happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's a real person!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:44.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, the Palm-top Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:46.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a student here until last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:49.24,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's Takasu-senpai's girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:50.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:22:02.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There exists in this world something\Nno one has ever seen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:06.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's gentle, and so very sweet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:11.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...That a glimpse is all it takes\Nto make a person crave it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:15.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why it's never been seen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.85,0:22:18.31,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why this world has kept it hidden.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.31,0:22:20.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Making it difficult to obtain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:23.98,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But one day, it will be found.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.46,0:22:42.88,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By the one person who is meant to find it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.34,0:22:46.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:48.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to surprise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.93,0:22:52.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you grown?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.14,0:22:55.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single millimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.14,0:22:56.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So sue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:22:57.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:22:59.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.57,0:23:07.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Tai—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:12.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How can you say something so\Nembarrassing in broad daylight!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:15.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to wait for the\Nright m-mood or s-situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.33,0:23:18.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because that's how it works.{\i0}
